root: ^Hiya, farmer. Just kidding, I know you aren't one.
^How would you do farming with only two legs? I can't even think of it happening.
^Oh, have you checked out both our farms? There's one here, and another one to the west.
^You should go look around. I think you'll like it!
^You'll have to go the long way around, though. The two farms are blocked off from one another.
